                        <p>“Playing for an audience outside the black metal community is nothing new for us,” Hunt-Hendrix said. “But we have never performed for people this far outside the black metal community.”</p>
<p>At the Coffeehouse, Liturgy will perform for students who have little experience with black metal.</p>
<p>“Liturgy is the first black metal band to perform here,” said Wyngaarden. “Other metal bands have played, but black metal is something that Duke has not had an opportunity to see.”</p>

